{
  "stem": "23090.6",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And that's how I lost my mother and my sister.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So when I got that news, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I lost the hope, a very wonderful thing that I always hoped would happen, the miracle that would happen.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And it was not to be.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And this is how I came to the United States.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "This is what happened to me, and I miss-- my Aunt Winifred Fryer was a very wonderful person.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "She helped me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "When I came here, I was an animal.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I didn't know how to hold a fork, a knife.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I was-- I couldn't get along with anyone.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I had to go to Bellefaire, which is an orphanage here for disturbed children.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I had to be in Bellefaire because I could not be contained.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I was under psychiatric care, children's psychiatric care, Dr.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Oscar Markey.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "I went through the process of so-called rehab.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "I don't know how I rehabilitated myself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "I can honestly tell you I don't know how I even came to be able to do an interview like this on the basis of-- of coping with what had happened because I wasn't put in some sort of a school, a processing school, to be able to come out and be able to say to you that I'm over this.",
      "word_count": 61
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "But that's just another part of survival.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And with the bad comes some good.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And believe it or not, it was-- in my lifetime, apparently, I was destined to see another war and I was drafted into the Korean War.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I wound up in Korea as an American soldier.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] and the beat goes on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And life had to go on.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
